    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏状态</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（本部分将定期更新，为玩家提供关于游戏当前开发状态及未来方向的清晰和诚实的概述。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>垂直切片</strong><br>本次<i>垂直切片</i>展示了《Lancelot》的核心机制、设计、艺术方向以及预期的游戏氛围和玩法。游戏目前由两人团队开发，使用了一些预制的3D资源和动画。艺术风格和玩法范围可能会根据玩家和潜在投资者的反馈而调整。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Lancelot》是对亚瑟王传说的黑暗重塑，将兰斯洛特设为主角，而亚瑟王成为终极反派。故事分为多个章节展开，每章重新讲述传说中的关键时刻，重点聚焦兰斯洛特、梅林和亚瑟王。玩家将在熟悉的故事中体验黑暗的转折，沉浸于一个传奇与道德模糊交织的世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/5a8791d91f255def35f4741739090d3a.poster.avif?t=1734963593\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/5a8791d91f255def35f4741739090d3a.webm?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/5a8791d91f255def35f4741739090d3a.mp4?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了追求以机制深度为核心的简化RPG体验，而非繁多的物品和构建，我们实施了独特的系统来定义兰斯洛特的游戏玩法：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诅咒铠甲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兰斯洛特和其他角色被<i>诅咒铠甲</i>束缚，这赋予了他们力量，但也带来危险。在战斗失败后，兰斯洛特可以利用诅咒复活，增强耐久性和伤害输出，但会逐渐接近永久死亡。这种类Roguelike机制在完全失败后会重置故事进度，为每次战斗增添紧张感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/66c24b0029abe3c87b6cc15668dac22a.poster.avif?t=1734963593\" width=594 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/66c24b0029abe3c87b6cc15668dac22a.webm?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/66c24b0029abe3c87b6cc15668dac22a.mp4?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>元素亲和</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兰斯洛特的体力和法力合并为一个资源条。体力可以恢复，用于物理能力；法力支持元素技能，但无法通过常规手段恢复，需付出代价。玩家需要在物理与魔法状态之间战略性切换，在力量和谨慎之间找到平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/b8cf9c05eba82d92b49cf65887ac1b9b.poster.avif?t=1734963593\" width=594 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/b8cf9c05eba82d92b49cf65887ac1b9b.webm?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/b8cf9c05eba82d92b49cf65887ac1b9b.mp4?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自适应武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兰斯洛特可用的武器种类有限，但可通过多种方式使用，这与诅咒铠甲和元素亲和系统息息相关。一条随着武器使用填充的技能条为战斗和探索提供更多选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/51ceb0645d0dbcf686de5d366214f96c.poster.avif?t=1734963593\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/51ceb0645d0dbcf686de5d366214f96c.webm?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/51ceb0645d0dbcf686de5d366214f96c.mp4?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特时间系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事在固定的天数内展开，兰斯洛特的选择会影响战斗遭遇和世界事件。某些敌人在特定日子可能不会出现，这让前进变得容易，但会在之后遇到更强挑战。环境因素如雨水也会影响战斗，例如对抗火属性敌人时占据优势，为游戏加入动态战略层面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/5a49f5c12217bc0082bc866b79c1f41f.poster.avif?t=1734963593\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/5a49f5c12217bc0082bc866b79c1f41f.webm?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302410/extras/5a49f5c12217bc0082bc866b79c1f41f.mp4?t=1734963593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
